##The day that can get online lesson only, everybody is anxious to move into the world

Micro Signal thelivings

The function introduction, reconstructs our life with the narrative beauty.

See The teacher in the class group of other children to listen to the Internet class seriously do notes, their own children are listening to the Internet class while sleeping, do not take out the pen, the mothers immediately exploded. The fire spread to the child's father, grandparents also came to persuade, the result is another family scuffle.

Photo: still from 72 hours in the school district

Before this Spring Festival, I never thought that we first-line teachers would have a day to work from home. Nor did I think that parents would have a day when they would put aside their work and devote themselves wholeheartedly to reading with them, there's GonNa be a day of crying and begging to go to school.
And all of a sudden,.

At the end of the first semester of 2019-2020, as the head teacher, I wrote on the students'report cards that the holidays would run from January 18 to February 8, and the next semester would start at 8:00 on February 9.
At that time, my mind a few days before the start of school to check the students in the Class Group of winter vacation homework, so as not to start teaching new content when they have to squeeze time to make up homework.
From there, it's a vacation to enjoy yourself -- as always -- with friends and family, new clothes for the kids, and a little family vacation, i'm happy just thinking about it. After handing out grades and saying good-bye to everyone, it's like handing the kids back to their parents.
The first day of the holiday, we teaching and Research Group of a few little sisters together with children to go shopping for dinner, a good round. At the end of the break-up, we also agreed to take a few days to see a movie. But before I could make it to the movies, the news of pneumonia was all over the news.
When the news came that the city was closed, masks and disinfectant could not be bought, and no one could go out. Word got around, and people got scared. But even so, I also did not expect the following winter vacation will be spent like that.

Busyness and tension seem to start all of a sudden.
On January 24, the day of the New Year's Eve, our family was preparing a New Year's Eve dinner, when the mobile phone suddenly rang. The leadership asked in the working group that every head teacher should immediately count the situation of the Hubei students in the class: whether they have returned to Hubei for the New Year, have contact with relatives in Hubei, the student's current home address, parents work unit, the student's current physical condition and so on. If there is, you must report it immediately.
I hurriedly asked others in the working group: "The whole of Hubei to check? Not Only Wuhan? "
Colleagues you a word I a word, a variety of news retweets and screenshots all emerged, all the way down to see that this disease is not hanging a few bottles of salt water can be good, and spread very fast.
I immediately opened the computer out of the class information, carefully check the class information. I have a class of Hubei Students, the phone call, they have bought a house in the city, this year did not return to Hubei New Year, Hubei Relatives did not come.
Then the tension took the place of all the joy of the new year and the family reunion was cancelled.
My father is a restless man who goes to the vegetable market every day, i kindly advised: "The market so many people, if one person infected, then the entire market may be infected, the home is not without vegetables, do not go these days. " He was also reluctant to, "Wuhan is so far away from us, afraid of what? "
"All right, you put your mask on. " I advised him, but he was reluctant. "You have to wear a mask when you go out to buy food. Don't you have to wear a mask when you start school? You won't be able to attend class. "
On January 26th, on the second day of the Lunar New Year, the Education Department issued an emergency notice to delay the start of the school year, as if it had never happened in years.
When she heard that winter vacation would be extended, her daughter was so happy that she could watch cartoons all the time, sleep in in peace, and of course eat on the Sofa all day long. Winter vacation homework has long done, pure play of life let her happy mouth from ear to ear.
And I panicked even more.

What if the delay in the start of the semester means that the course content for the next semester can not be taught in time? One semester to teach the content is fixed, short time content, students can not digest, teachers and parents are anxious. The class group also began to have parents to ask.
Soon, there was a policy: All teachers designed first week prep plans in advance and sent them to students, who studied at home, and assigned them to watch the online sessions and complete assignments, "No class, no suspension. ".
To design a teaching plan, to teach online, but the current holiday at home, hand books, materials are not complete, how to design? But can only wear a mask gloves, heavily armed to the school to turn over a few books back.
The road was empty, with only a few cars passing by and not a single passer-by. As I passed the school gate, the volunteer in the red vest was about to take his temperature and look at his ID card when someone called out my name, it was my colleague, Little Florida. He was standing there with a mask and goggles on, and I almost didn't recognize him.
"Are you volunteering? " I asked curiously.
"Our little class teacher doesn't have to design a schedule, and he's just sitting around doing nothing. Are you going to get a book? I just saw Xiao Hu go by. "
"Yes, are you on duty at night, too? "
"Yes, the second half of the night is cold, and the first half of the night is a little better. "
I thought of myself sleeping till dawn, but they were watching the cold night, and I hastened to urge myself to cheer up.

I've been thinking for a long time about how I should take this English class. Instead of teaching the children face to face, without looking at their tiny mouths, without getting them to stand up and read me the new sentence patterns, and without interactive feedback, I always feel a little insecure.
Think of the usual class, the teacher is standing there staring at everyone, the children will secretly leave a small business, do a small action, now the teacher is not around, it must be a "wide business, do big action" scene. At the thought of it, I even imagined the faces of some naughty children in my class.
To be on the safe side, I decided to first arrange the simplest transcriptions and follow-ups in the planning of the preview. Even so, it's a little scary... I don't know about middle school students, but for elementary school students with little self control, this new approach to distance learning is really not reassuring.
After designing the course, I said to my daughter, "go and take out the books your mother lent you and review them a few times. Mark out the parts that you can't read with a pen, and it will be much easier to learn by then. " But my daughter kept her mouth shut and did not move her body. I just want to lose temper, was held down by the husband, "to believe the children... . New Year's, do not easily scold the children. " I can only hold back, well, believe you.
January 30, the sixth day of the Lunar New Year, the school announced the next term language to learn by heart the text. If you memorize it at home, you'll save time after school starts. As the head teacher, I hurriedly arranged in the class group, "please put down the mobile phone, IPAD and TV remote control, the next semester's text by heart it. "
I hovered in the crowd, but after a long day, only a handful of parents responded. Most parents think it's still early. Take it easy for a few days.
Parents are right, only the sixth, I also want to relax a few days, but the current situation is not optimistic.
On February 1st, one message after another in the work group, the school has arranged several tasks in succession: "Each head teacher, please report the students' body temperature in the class group and make a daily report. ". If you don't hear from anyone in the class by 10:00, call and make sure everyone reports it."
Then there are: "The head teacher, please check the Wuhan area personnel, January 10 class students family members have been to Wuhan or Wuhan personnel contact. ". If there is, report the main information of family members quickly, and make sure that you work from side to side, so that there are no omissions and no dead ends."
So, Qq, SMS, telephone, inquire about the situation of each student, each head teacher is busy like a telephone operator.
Not finished statistics, I was informed: "The class teacher, the near future will be online study schedule sent to students, to ensure that the layout of February 3 to start online learning. "
The small group of teaching and Research Group immediately livened up: Are we going to be an anchor? Like an old video site where you double-click on 666 and swipe a rocket? Oh, my God, this is so exciting. Do you want to get up in the morning and do some makeup? Are you nervous? I feel like I'm being lectured by the whole country. I hope I don't become an Internet celebrity?
As soon as we saw the first session, we realized that we were overthinking it -- as if the first session was a warm-up before class, as it was mostly about extra-curricular reading and extra-curricular activities by some of the best teachers in the area, all we have to do is remind the students to look.
That's a huge relief.

By the time online classes begin on Feb. 3, parents are busy, too.
When I woke up in the morning, I began to urge parents to report their children's body temperature. On this kind of day, parents would like to sleep a little longer. But I can't wait any longer, so I have to make phone calls one by one.
At 9:00 in the morning, the online class began, too many people logged on to the website, the server crashed, the parents tried everything but almost no one could successfully log on, and all came to ask me: "What about the teacher? I couldn't open it. I tried for an hour and couldn't log on. "
I am also very anxious, my daughter is to take online classes, mobile phones, computers, ipads, one by one try, all no good. 4G, wireless switching in turn, no. All I could do was say, "it's okay, it's a recording, you can watch it later. " All morning, I couldn't even go to the bathroom without putting my gadgets down.
I am on the edge of my seat here, my daughter is also a bit anxious, I assigned the task she may not be very concerned about, but the teacher's words or listen. Every once in a while, he comes to me and says, "is it open? " I'm even more worried.
Finally until noon, less people, I finally opened the school's web page, each class tried again, can play, hurry in the class group announced the good news.
The teachers recording classes are well-known teachers in our region, usually our teachers hear them a lesson is very difficult, it is also a learning opportunity for me.
Chinese is about the appreciation of extra-curricular reading, English is extra-curricular picture book. The teachers spoke very carefully. My daughter had read both of the books, so she enjoyed them. Then I thought, if you haven't read the book of the students must be confused, now the courier has stopped, want to buy a book can not buy, really for the class of children sweat.

At this point, the class teacher group also sent New News, need to fill out the "new crown epidemic prevention and control of the whole table. ". This is a very detailed statistical table, in addition to the usual name, sex, contact number, ID number, place of origin and current home address, they also included questions about where students had been during the holidays, whether they had come into contact with people in the affected areas, whether they had left the area, where they had gone, when they had returned, whether they had been quarantined and whether they were healthy.
My head just got so big. It's a daunting task -- Florida -- not every parent fills out a spreadsheet, and not every family has a computer on hand. Some of the students back home don't even have Internet access to their cell phones. There are some children parents are not at home, with grandparents living, grandparents can not even read the word, the home of electronic products only the elderly machine. It was too much for me to fill out such a form.
Several head teachers could not help complaining: usually in school, we can also print out the form, parents take a pen to fill out, the next day the teacher collected to fill in their own. What are we gonNA do now.
Can Grumble to grumble, hand can not stop, real-time urge, real-time fill, real-time response, like Taobao shop customer service, afraid of late response, parents and can not be contacted.
Sure enough, there will always be a few parents are too upset to fill in a gas, head teachers can only be carefully reviewed, confirmed by telephone. I'll do the summary after I fill out the detailed form. I do their own side of the work, but also to fill the daughter, one day down, straight black eyes.

In the evening, she chatted with a young sister who was chosen by the Education Bureau to take a third-grade math class. She posted a complaint on her facebook page. "I'm so busy... I don't go to bed until four or five in the morning for several days, and I have to get up at eight or nine in the morning. "
I asked her, why don't you go to bed until five or six?
"during the day the children have to go to school to think and the new oriental 'close class' , and there is so much homework to do, I have to accompany, morning, noon and evening three meals to wait on. I can record my own lessons in the evening. If I make a mistake or have a pause, I have to re-record it. After recording, I feel that I have to revise and re-record any part of my lessons. If I don't pay attention, it's 5:00 or 6:00 in the morning. If I sleep until 8:00 or 9:00, I have to start online lessons with my children... it's too hard."
Little sister said, when recording the net class no blackboard, do not show the teacher's face, mainly to PPT talk, students will see PPT knowledge points on it. "The principal asked me to come up with the best class design, so I recorded it a million times and tried it on my own son. "
Usually in class, the teacher and students face-to-face communication, whether it is eye or language, at any time according to the reaction of the students to the class the children do not have a solid enough place to practice a few times. Now, there are no students in the course, the difficulties depend on the teacher according to their own experience to grasp. It's boring to keep asking questions and answering them yourself. And as a primary school teacher, in order to let the children do not so fast, but also specifically designed a lot of interesting links.
It wasn't easy.

On February 10th, the normal start of the school year began.
Prior to the school arrangement of online learning is only extra-curricular knowledge, you can look around, really do not want to see also not forced. Now is the knowledge on the textbook really start to learn, parents are very important. All the electronic devices in the House are prepared in advance, books can be borrowed, can not be borrowed to download e-books, there is a printer for the family to print the necessary materials, also in this special period to prepare enough stationery, notebooks, exercise books, go all out to cooperate with the children's learning.
As usual, I woke up in the morning began to count his class students'physical condition, telephone Qq two-pronged fill out the daily feel the dynamic table. When the gap, still in sleep to pull up their children, throw in front of the computer, see her face did not wake up absent-minded look, hot temper immediately came up.
The parents of the students in my class must be the same as me.
8:40 net class began, the content is very rich, there are Chinese class, math class, English class, art class, music class, physical education and information class, as colorful as school classes. However, the website is still stuck badly. If the previous week's class was dominated by extra-curricular knowledge, it wouldn't matter if parents didn't pay attention. This time it really is the new knowledge in the textbook. It's not OK to drop any of it, the parents were so anxious to curse when they couldn't get on the web site.
But, you know, no matter how hard you try, the site just gets stuck. Anxious parents kept asking the teacher, "why is it so stuck? Can't you do something about it? How can we learn if the books are still not distributed? Can't you send them to us by express delivery? "
But we are also very helpless, express already stopped, how send?
Soon, a teacher can upload the video disk, and then sent to the class group, so do not worry about. Soon, the teachers are taking action, the class group has a complete online class video, parents finally calm down.
As an English teacher, I carefully watched and learned English class, picture quality clear, pronunciation clear, heavy and difficult points prominent, each link compact, the most rare is, a slip of the tongue did not appear. Put Heart to heart, the teacher must have also recorded countless times, to have such an effect.
However, there is nothing wrong with online classes, but whether kids will buy into them is another matter.
Soon, one parent in the class group complained, "it's a good thing I have two nostrils to vent, or I'd be mad. My Kid, I let him take Internet lessons by himself, just opened the door to see, actually fell asleep! "
"What are you, my guy pulls the progress bar to the end and then sneaks in a game while I'm not looking, and I walk up to him and I don't even see it. "
"The same, are not serious, children AH, a few can control their own, or adults to watch. "
……
I didn't bother to reply, so I took a look at my baby, ate some chips and went to class, saying, "it's not pretty, " as I stood outside the door, I almost vomited blood, as if it was a class, not as good as your cartoons, of course.

After class, the teacher will assign the homework and remind the students to submit the homework.
This is a big problem, some parents said, we do not have books can not copy, I rushed to the Nth e-textbooks in the class group; some parents said, we do not book, do we risk going out to buy it? I settle for nothing more than a piece of paper, and parents say we all have to go to work, the kids don't have a cell phone to see the group's homework, can you stall for a few days? Individual parents also said, we are isolated in the field, what do not matter, a few days to complete it? I can only answer: "Line Line Line line line, as long as the normal start-up before the completion of the line. "
I asked my children, who only have their old-age phones, if they had a smartphone, and they answered, "No, I don't do homework. " I Speechless (TV series) , what can I say at a time like this? I had to write it down myself, and I gave it to him alone when school started. There's more to it than meets the eye.
Schools also know the difficulties of parents, let the head teacher in the Class Group send notice: Homework do not do rigid requirements, the content of online classes, teachers will focus on re-teaching after the start of school, not too anxious.
The problem, then, is that it makes anxious parents even more anxious. Teachers in the group said: "suspension of school, as long as the children are not in waste time, in learning, is suspended without suspension. ". Learning a book is learning, reading a few books is learning, learning a skill is learning, no hard work."
And so, the little ones immediately began to take chicken feathers as an Arrow, as if a daughter was holding a homework sent by their head teacher and said, "mom, look, the teacher said that the conditional students write down the words after writing them down, you see, not everyone has to hand them in, conditional, you see? " I could only stare at her: "You have no conditions? "? A pen or a book?"
"I'm short on time. I want to watch cartoons. "
So angry that I immediately took out a feather duster, "several children are silent, but also all right, you still tell me this? "

Right now, all kinds of online classes and intensive classes are driving parents crazy.
The original Weekday, children in school, parents work outside, out of sight, angry is the teacher's business. The parent-child relationship is less acrimonious when the parent watches the child do homework for a while at night. Now the epidemic is not over, most of the parents have not yet started, at home watching the The Hours, all the shortcomings are exposed, it is hard not to get angry.
What's more, the scariest thing in the world is that it is easier to feel like a bad boy than a better darling. I used to think my kids were cute and smart, but compared to the nerds, I thought my kids were so bad, I just wanted to beat them up.
Parents often put their outstanding children in the friends circle, said how many papers done today, how many times got full marks, self-taught has learned lesson number, the following is a group of jealous parents.
See other children's daily excellent clock work, handwriting is also consciously timely, and his family a pile of errors, handwriting is not correct also tardy, parents anxiety will soon become angry in the child; See The teacher in the class group of other children to listen to the Internet class seriously do notes, their own children are listening to the Internet class while sleeping, do not take out the pen, how can the mothers not be angry.
The mother gets angry, the fire will spread to the father immediately, once the child to hit the child with a feather duster, grandparents will certainly come to persuade, inevitably is a family scuffle.
There are parents in the class group feedback said: "A network class down to master the content is not much, not as real class teaching. ". We have to teach it again after class. We can teach it in Chinese and math. We can't even pronounce English properly. I'm so anxious these days."
Several other parents agreed. "Our family is not aware of it. When I am busy with my own affairs, he starts to be lazy, doesn't write carefully and has a high rate of mistakes. Let's start school early. Teaching children is a real headache. "
The teachers talked about it and thought it would be good for the students to finish their online lessons and not much homework was assigned. Other colleagues have echoed, after the beginning of the school to teach again, these days let them a little bit involved in understanding.
"Hang in there, let's get through this. " In the end, we can only comfort each other.
I mean, parents really don't have to be so anxious. I told you countless times in the group: "It's okay, the text teacher will speak again, will not be out of step, the way is more difficult than. "
But a parent's anxiety can not be dispelled with a word or two.
That day, I saw a friend in the circle of friends for the children's schedule, 7:00 to get up, 9:30 to go to bed, this section is full of all kinds of online classes, learning, thinking, New Oriental, school, and after-school art training.
I couldn't help but ask her, your kid's in third grade, and you grabbed him that hard?
"Don't mention it. I gave the boy a beating today. I can't help the way he's taking his time. Winter vacation in everyone is fighting, if I let him play, to the beginning of school is not YTHT, than others a big gap? I'm in a hurry too."
That's what they call "overtaking on a curve. " I'm worried about the kid.
At my house, I followed my daughter's advice and didn't enroll her for extra-curricular classes during the winter vacation, so the anxiety wasn't that serious. But I kept an eye on her classes, attending classes on time, pressing her to do her homework, and submitting it on time, but didn't check her homework until it was true, unless she was under the impression that it was a real error rate.
Of course, even then, there are still some wild goose chases, but that's about it.

Epilogue

A while ago, there was a joke in the circle of friends that everyone became a cook, a nurse became a soldier, a teacher became an anchor, a parent became a head teacher, and only the children were still, as if she were a god.
Daughter complained every day: "Say what delayed school, I see is early school, my winter vacation is not how to play, day after day shut at home by you scold, not cool. "
I stared at her, I also is not it, both parents and teachers, I can understand, the teachers feel Internet class is not happy enough scratch scratch, have the strength to try their best in the classroom, looking forward to a quick start of school; Parents look at their kids every day, understand the difficulties of disciplining them, and look forward to the start of school; while the children are long past being shut in, and ask countless times every day, "when can I go out to school? "
The trees in the south of the Yangtze River are already sprouting new shoots and the flowers on their branches are gradually opening up. Spring is coming soon, and the cold winter will pass. I believe that the epidemic will be over soon, everything will be fine, we look forward to the beginning of the school should also be in sight.

Now the epidemic is not over, most of the parents have not yet started, at home watching the The Hours, all the shortcomings are exposed, it is hard not to get angry.
What's more, the scariest thing in the world is that it is easier to feel like a bad boy than a better darling. I used to think my kids were cute and smart, but compared to the nerds, I thought my kids were so bad, I just wanted to beat them up.
Parents often put their outstanding children in the friends circle, said how many papers done today, how many times got full marks, self-taught has learned lesson number, the following is a group of jealous parents.
See other children's daily excellent clock work, handwriting is also consciously timely, and his family a pile of errors, handwriting is not correct also tardy, parents anxiety will soon become angry in the child; See The teacher in the class group of other children to listen to the Internet class seriously do notes, their own children are listening to the Internet class while sleeping, do not take out the pen, how can the mothers not be angry.
The mother gets angry, the fire will spread to the father immediately, once the child to hit the child with a feather duster, grandparents will certainly come to persuade, inevitably is a family scuffle.
There are parents in the class group feedback said: "A network class down to master the content is not much, not as real class teaching. ". We have to teach it again after class. We can teach it in Chinese and math. We can't even pronounce English properly. I'm so anxious these days."
Several other parents agreed. "Our family is not aware of it. When I am busy with my own affairs, he starts to be lazy, doesn't write carefully and has a high rate of mistakes. Let's start school early. Teaching children is a real headache. "
The teachers talked about it and thought it would be good for the students to finish their online lessons and not much homework was assigned. Other colleagues have echoed, after the beginning of the school to teach again, these days let them a little bit involved in understanding.
"Hang in there, let's get through this. " In the end, we can only comfort each other.
I mean, parents really don't have to be so anxious. I told you countless times in the group: "It's okay, the text teacher will speak again, will not be out of step, the way is more difficult than. "
But a parent's anxiety can not be dispelled with a word or two.
That day, I saw a friend in the circle of friends for the children's schedule, 7:00 to get up, 9:30 to go to bed, this section is full of all kinds of online classes, learning, thinking, New Oriental, school, and after-school art training.
I couldn't help but ask her, your kid's in third grade, and you grabbed him that hard?
"Don't mention it. I gave the boy a beating today. I can't help the way he's taking his time. Winter vacation in everyone is fighting, if I let him play, to the beginning of school is not YTHT, than others a big gap? I'm in a hurry too."
That's what they call "overtaking on a curve. " I'm worried about the kid.
At my house, I followed my daughter's advice and didn't enroll her for extra-curricular classes during the winter vacation, so the anxiety wasn't that serious. But I kept an eye on her classes, attending classes on time, pressing her to do her homework, and submitting it on time, but didn't check her homework until it was true, unless she was under the impression that it was a real error rate.
Of course, even then, there are still some wild goose chases, but that's about it.

Right now, all kinds of online classes and intensive classes are driving parents crazy.

Epilogue

A while ago, there was a joke in the circle of friends that everyone became a cook, a nurse became a soldier, a teacher became an anchor, a parent became a head teacher, and only the children were still, as if she were a god.
Daughter complained every day: "Say what delayed school, I see is early school, my winter vacation is not how to play, day after day shut at home by you scold, not cool. "
I stared at her, I also is not it, both parents and teachers, I can understand, the teachers feel Internet class is not happy enough scratch scratch, have the strength to try their best in the classroom, looking forward to a quick start of school; Parents look at their kids every day, understand the difficulties of disciplining them, and look forward to the start of school; while the children are long past being shut in, and ask countless times every day, "when can I go out to school? "
The trees in the south of the Yangtze River are already sprouting new shoots and the flowers on their branches are gradually opening up. Spring is coming soon, and the cold winter will pass. I believe that the epidemic will be over soon, everything will be fine, we look forward to the beginning of the school should also be in sight.
